Change Log
==========

Release 
--------------------------------
* Fix copyright information.

Release 0.014 - (April 16, 2010)
--------------------------------
* Add raster plot, figure resizing functions.
* Add bandpass test signal generator.
* Include mtit function from Matlab Central.
* Add fft-based convolution.
* Add bandpass test signal generator.

Release 0.013 - (January 07, 2010)
----------------------------------
* Plotting bug fix.

Release 0.012 - (October 26, 2009)
----------------------------------
* Make time array construction consistently use a fixed time step.

Release 0.011 - (October 02, 2009)
----------------------------------
* Make random phase of generated test signal uniformly distributed
  over the range [0,2*pi].
* Improve plotting.
* Improve organization of toolbox files.

Release 0.01 - (May 08, 2009)
-----------------------------
* First public release.
